    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Add the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lemon wedges </strong>to a small bowl</p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 3,
