      "instruction": "<p>Add 3 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[4 1/2 tbsp]</span> [6 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> to a large plate with with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Press your <strong>salmon fillet[s]</strong> into the<strong> </strong>flour so the fish is evenly coated, shaking off any excess</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
